on for spin is thus ideal for treatment\nof higher order spin dependent sectors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Jan 2015 20:54:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Aug 2015 08:24:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 5 Oct 2015 23:30:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-07"}
