 include catalogs of clusters, background galaxies, remaining\nunselected candidates, and synthetic cluster simulations, making all\ninformation publicly available to the community. The catalog published here\nserves as the definitive base data product for PHAT cluster science, providing\na census of star clusters in an L$^*$ spiral galaxy with unmatched sensitivity\nand quality.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Jan 2015 21:00:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
